# 2064 Die Geschichte der Cypherpunks

## File structure

chapters/ | The chapters of the book. Change texts here.
parts/ | Include file showing how the chapters are grouped
html/ | HTML pages of all parts
mail/ | Subscriber data
tools/ | Conversion and mailing tools

## Utilities & Functions

### make 

Builds all parts of the book. They are stored in html/.

### make publish

Publishes changed html pages in wordpress. Password file tools/wppwd needed.

### ./sendparts.sh

Sends all current parts to all subscribers listed in the file mail/mail.json
Only sends mail out on mailing days. And only sends them out once.